alldb.table_sql: SELECT ID as id, START_DATE_ as startdate, RATE_HALF as ratehalf, RATE_ONE as rateone, RATE_THREE as ratethree, RATE_FIVE as ratefive, RATE_ABOVEFIVE as rateabovefive, BASE_RATE_HALF as baseratehalf, BASE_RATE_ONE as baserateone, BASE_RATE_THREE as baseratethree, BASE_RATE_FIVE as baseratefive, BASE_RATE_ABOVEFIVE as baserateabovefive, IS_CLOSE isclose, CREATOR_ as creator, CREATE_DATE as creatordate, MODIFY_DATE as modifydate, MODIFICATOR_ as modificator FROM FUND_STANDARD_INTEREST WHERE 1=1
